        Ce que disent nos lecteurs
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-yellow-400 mb-3">
            <span>‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê</span>
